Its a school project in C with the ncurses lib.
We had to code a Tetris game with a debug mod, this debug mod allow us to create new forms.

To create new forms you have to create a '.tetriminos' file in tetriminos directory.

The two first number are the sizes of the tetriminos
and the third is the color. The tetrimino is composed by '*' and ' '.

Type --help for help

Good game !! :D